OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tue 24 Mar to Thu 2 Apr
OL,6,FChangeable and at times unsettled
OL,7,Fconditions for many parts of the UK at
OL,8,Fthe start of this period, as areas of
OL,9,Flow pressure and their associated
OL,10,Ffrontal zones run close to or over the
OL,11,FUK. These are likely to be most active
OL,12,Fin the north and somewhat weaker
OL,13,Ffurther south, closer to a ridge of
OL,14,Fhigh pressure extending northeast from
OL,15,Fthe subtropical Atlantic. There is
OL,16,Falso potential for a period of widely
OL,17,Fwindy weather during the first part of
OL,18,Fthis period. By the turn of the month
OL,19,Fhigh pressure may become rather more
OL,20,Fdominant once again with plenty of dry
OL,21,Fweather, but with some overnight fog
OL,22,Fand frost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
